steps.instruction:
### Prep
- Preheat oven to 400F
- Cut Apples into small pieces (2 cups); toss with 1.5 tablespoons of the cinnamon sugar


### Steps
1. Open can of rolls (do not separate them) instead unroll the entire dough on a baking sheet
2. Press the edges of the rolls together to form a crust about 9x13 inches 
3. Sprinkle apples over crust
4. Bake for 6 to 7 minutes
5. Top with granola
6. Bake for another 6 to 7 minutes
7. Let cool for 2 to 3 minutes
8. Place icing (from the cinnamon rolls) in a bowl and microwave on 50% power for 20 to 30 seconds
9. Drizzle on pizza
10. Sprinkle the last of the of the cinnamon-sugar on top
